<P>
Ireland's caretaker Prime Minister Charles Haughey, abandoning his resistance 
to a coalition government, began a week of talks with Desmond O' Malley, leader 
of the Progressive Democrats in an effort to form a new government. "A new 
political era is in sight," O' Malley told deputies in Parliament as his small 
