HOUSING AUTHORITY; SOUTH CENTRAL LOS ANGELES; LOS ANGELES -- DEVELOPMENT AND 
REDEVELOPMENT; LOS ANGELES -- TRANSPORTATION; HOUSING -- LOS ANGELES; TRAFFIC 
-- LOS ANGELES; WELFARE PROGRAMS -- LOS ANGELES; SUBSIDIZED HOUSING; CRIME 
PREVENTION; POLICE PATROLS; TRAFFIC MANAGEMENT; TRUCKS 
</P>
