<HEADLINE>
<P>
WORD OF MOUTH: A WEEKEND FOR SANTA BARBARA WINERIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By RUTH REICHL 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
If you've been planning a trip to Santa Barbara, this weekend would be a good 
time to take it. All 22 wineries in the county are holding an open house. 
Special events include tours of wineries normally closed to the public, meals 
with various wine makers, tastings of older wines. . . . 
</P>
<P>
Sunday features include a free all-day barbecue at Ballard Canyon Winery with 
country music, and a bouillabaisse festival at the Brander Vineyard ($10 per 
person). For more information, call the various Santa Barbara wineries, or 
(805) 688-0881 and (805) 688-6144. RUTH REICHL 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
