<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Times Mirror Buys Training Firm: Times Mirror said it acquired Kaset Inc. of 
Tampa, Fla., a company that trains employees in customer relations. Terms were 
not disclosed. Times Mirror already owns firms that specialize in sales 
training and supervisory training. Kaset works for utilities, financial 
institutions, telecommunications companies, and state and municipal 
governments. Times Mirror also announced that it completed the previously 
reported acquisition of the stock of Chillicothe Cablevision Inc. 
</P>
</TEXT>
